function copyToClipboard(text){if(navigator.clipboard&&navigator.clipboard.writeText){navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).catch(err=>{fallbackCopy(text);});}else{fallbackCopy(text);}}function fallbackCopy(text){const textArea=document.createElement('textarea');textArea.value=text;textArea.style.position='fixed';textArea.style.left='-999999px';textArea.style.top='-999999px';document.body.appendChild(textArea);textArea.focus();textArea.select();try{document.execCommand('copy');}catch(err){console.error('复制失败:',err);}document.body.removeChild(textArea);}function initToast(){if(!document.getElementById('toast')){toast=document.createElement('div');toast.id='toast';toast.className='toast';document.body.appendChild(toast);}}let currentTimeout=0;function showToast(message){const toast=document.getElementById('toast');if(!toast)return;clearTimeout(currentTimeout);toast.textContent=message;toast.classList.add('isShow');currentTimeout=setTimeout(()=>toast.classList.remove('isShow'),2000);}function enablePageScroll(){document.body.classList.remove('noScroll');}function disablePageScroll(){document.body.classList.add('noScroll');}(()=>{const isMobile=/Android|webOS|iPhone|iPad|iPod|BlackBerry|IEMobile|Opera Mini|MicroMessenger/i.test(navigator.userAgent);const FAVORITES_KEY='emojiFavorites';let favorites=[];let emojiDataCache=null;let selectedResultIndex=-1;document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function(){initToast();initMainItems();initCopy();initSidebar();initFavorite();initSearch();initShare();});function initMainItems(){const mainItems=document.querySelectorAll('.mainItem');if(mainItems.length===0)return;mainItems.forEach((item)=>{item.dataset.emoji=item.querySelector('.mainEmoji').textContent;addCopyButton(item);addFavoriteButton(item);});}function initCopy(){document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{let button=e.target;if(button.closest('.jsCopyButton')){button=button.closest('.jsCopyButton');}if(button.classList.contains('jsCopyButton')){const emoji=button.dataset.emoji;e.preventDefault();e.stopPropagation();copyToClipboard(emoji);showToast('已复制：'+emoji);}});}function addCopyButton(item){const buttonContainer=document.createElement('span');buttonContainer.classList.add('copyButtonContainer');if(!isMobile){buttonContainer.classList.add('isDesktop');}const button=document.createElement('button');button.classList.add('copyButton','jsCopyButton');button.textContent='复制';button.dataset.emoji=item.querySelector('.mainEmoji').textContent;buttonContainer.appendChild(button);item.appendChild(buttonContainer);}function initSidebar(){const menuToggle=document.getElementById('menuToggle');if(menuToggle){menuToggle.addEventListener('click',toggleSidebar);}const overlay=document.getElementById('overlay');if(overlay){overlay.addEventListener('click',closeSidebar);}const display=window.getComputedStyle(menuToggle).display;if(display!=='none'){document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{const el=e.target;const cl=el.classList;const isLink=cl.contains('sidebarLink')||cl.contains('sidebarSublink');const linkEl=el.closest('.sidebarItem')||el.closest('.sidebarSubitem');if(isLink||linkEl){closeSidebar(e);}});}const pageIndex=document.body.classList.contains('pageIndex');if(pageIndex){initSidebarAnchorLinks();}}function initSidebarAnchorLinks(){const categoryContent=document.getElementById('categoryContent');if(!categoryContent)return;const anchorMap={};const mainSections=document.querySelectorAll('.mainSection');mainSections.forEach(section=>{const sectionId=section.id;if(sectionId&&sectionId.startsWith('category-')){const categoryName=sectionId.replace('category-','');anchorMap[categoryName]=sectionId;const subcategories=section.querySelectorAll('.subcategory');subcategories.forEach(subcat=>{const subcatId=subcat.id;if(subcatId&&subcatId.startsWith('subcategory-')){const parts=subcatId.split('-');if(parts.length>=3){const subcatName=parts.slice(2).join('-');anchorMap[`${categoryName}-${subcatName}`]=subcatId;}}});}});const sidebarLinks=document.querySelectorAll('.sidebarLink');sidebarLinks.forEach(link=>{const sidebarItem=link.closest('.sidebarItem');if(!sidebarItem)return;const isTopLevel=link.classList.contains('isTop');const textSpan=link.querySelector('.sidebarText');if(!textSpan)return;const name=textSpan.textContent.trim();if(isTopLevel){if(anchorMap[name]){link.href=`#${anchorMap[name]}`;}}else{const parentItem=sidebarItem.parentElement.closest('.sidebarItem.isTop');if(parentItem){const parentLink=parentItem.querySelector('.sidebarLink.isTop');if(parentLink){const parentTextSpan=parentLink.querySelector('.sidebarText');if(parentTextSpan){const parentName=parentTextSpan.textContent.trim();const key=`${parentName}-${name}`;if(anchorMap[key]){link.href=`#${anchorMap[key]}`;}}}}}});}function toggleSidebar(e){const sidebar=document.getElementById('sidebar');const overlay=document.querySelector('.overlay');if(sidebar&&overlay){e.stopPropagation();sidebar.classList.toggle('isActive');overlay.classList.toggle('isActive');if(sidebar.classList.contains('isActive')){disablePageScroll();}else{enablePageScroll();}}}function closeSidebar(e){const sidebar=document.getElementById('sidebar');const overlay=document.querySelector('.overlay');if(sidebar&&overlay){sidebar.classList.remove('isActive');overlay.classList.remove('isActive');enablePageScroll();}}function initFavorite(){loadFavorites();updateFavorite();initToggleFavoriteSection();document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{const button=e.target;if(button.classList.contains('jsFavoriteButton')){e.preventDefault();e.stopPropagation();toggleFavorite(button);}});}function addFavoriteButton(item){const button=document.createElement('button');button.classList.add('favoriteStarButton','jsFavoriteButton');button.setAttribute('aria-label','收藏');button.dataset.emoji=item.querySelector('.mainEmoji').textContent;button.dataset.name=item.querySelector('.mainName').textContent;button.dataset.link=item.getAttribute('href');item.appendChild(button);}function updateFavoriteButtons(){const buttons=document.querySelectorAll('.jsFavoriteButton');buttons.forEach(setFavoriteButtonStatus);}function setFavoriteButtonStatus(button){const index=favorites.findIndex(item=>item.emoji===button.dataset.emoji);if(index>-1){button.classList.add('isActive');button.setAttribute('title','取消收藏');}else{button.classList.remove('isActive');button.setAttribute('title','收藏');}}function toggleFavorite(button){const emoji=button.dataset.emoji;const index=favorites.findIndex(item=>item.emoji===emoji);if(index>-1){favorites.splice(index,1);showToast('已取消收藏');}else{const emoji=button.dataset.emoji;const name=button.dataset.name;const link=button.dataset.link;if(emoji&&name&&link){favorites.push({emoji,name,link});showToast('✔️ 已收藏');}else{showToast('收藏失败');}}saveFavorites();updateFavorite();}function loadFavorites(){try{const stored=localStorage.getItem(FAVORITES_KEY);const favoritesData=stored ? JSON.parse(stored):[];if(Array.isArray(favoritesData)){favorites=favoritesData.filter(item=>item.emoji&&item.name&&item.link);}}catch(e){favorites=[];}}function saveFavorites(){localStorage.setItem(FAVORITES_KEY,JSON.stringify(favorites));}function updateFavoriteCount(){const countEl=document.getElementById('favoriteCount');const titleCountEl=document.getElementById('favoriteTitleCount');if(countEl){countEl.textContent=favorites.length;}if(titleCountEl){titleCountEl.textContent=favorites.length;}}function hideFavoriteSection(favoriteSection){if(favoriteSection&&favoriteSection.classList.contains('isShow')){favoriteSection.classList.remove('isShow');if(isMobile){enablePageScroll();}}}function createFavoriteSection(){const favoriteSection=document.createElement('div');favoriteSection.id='favoriteSection';favoriteSection.classList.add('favoriteSection','toggleShow');favoriteSection.innerHTML=`<h2 class="categoryHead"><span class="categoryTitle">⭐ 我的收藏</span><span class="categoryCount" id="favoriteTitleCount">0</span></h2><div class="mainGrid" id="favoriteGrid"></div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="favoriteCloseButton jsCloseFavoriteButton">✕</a>`;document.body.appendChild(favoriteSection);return favoriteSection;}function toggleFavoriteSection(favoriteSection){if(favoriteSection){favoriteSection.classList.toggle('isShow');if(isMobile){if(favoriteSection.classList.contains('isShow')){disablePageScroll();}else{enablePageScroll();}}}}function initToggleFavoriteSection(){const button=document.getElementById('favoriteToggle');const favoriteSection=document.getElementById('favoriteSection')||createFavoriteSection();updateFavoriteSection();if(button&&favoriteSection&&favoriteSection.classList.contains('toggleShow')){button.addEventListener('click',()=>toggleFavoriteSection(favoriteSection));document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{const isCloseButton=e.target.classList.contains('jsCloseFavoriteButton');const isToggleButton=e.target===button||e.target.closest('#favoriteToggle');if(isCloseButton||!e.target.closest('.favoriteSection')&&!isToggleButton){e.stopPropagation();hideFavoriteSection(favoriteSection);}});}}function updateFavoriteSection(){const grid=document.getElementById('favoriteGrid');if(!grid)return;if(favorites.length===0){grid.innerHTML='<p class="emptyMessage">暂无收藏，点击Emoji卡片上的☆添加收藏</p>';return;}const html=[];favorites.forEach(item=>{html.push(`<a href="${item.link}" class="mainItem"><span class="mainEmoji">${item.emoji}</span><span class="mainName">${item.name}</span><span class="copyButtonContainer${isMobile ? ' ':' isDesktop'}"><button class="copyButton jsCopyButton" data-emoji="${item.emoji}">复制</button></span><button class="favoriteStarButton jsFavoriteButton isActive" aria-label="收藏" data-emoji="${item.emoji}" data-name="${item.name}" data-link="${item.link}" title="取消收藏"></button></a>`);});grid.innerHTML=html.join('');}function updateFavorite(){updateFavoriteButtons();updateFavoriteCount();updateFavoriteSection();}function initSearch(){const form=document.getElementById('searchForm');const searchInput=document.getElementById('searchInput');if(searchInput){searchInput.addEventListener('focus',()=>{form.classList.add('isActive');if(searchInput.value.trim()){performSearch(searchInput.value.trim());}});searchInput.addEventListener('blur',()=>{form.classList.remove('isActive');});searchInput.addEventListener('keydown',handleSearchKeydown);searchInput.addEventListener('input',debounce(handleSearchInput,300));}const searchToggle=document.getElementById('searchToggle');const headerContent=document.getElementById('headerContent');if(searchToggle&&headerContent){searchToggle.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{headerContent.classList.add('isSearch');setTimeout(()=>searchInput.focus(),0);});document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{const el=e.target;const cl=el.classList;const isCloseBtn=cl.contains('searchCloseBtn');if(isCloseBtn){headerContent.classList.remove('isSearch');hideSearchResults();}});}document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{const resultBox=document.getElementById('searchResultBox');if(resultBox&&!e.target.closest('.searchBox')){hideSearchResults();}});}function debounce(func,wait){let timeout;return function(){const context=this;const args=arguments;clearTimeout(timeout);timeout=setTimeout(()=>func.apply(context,args),wait);};}function loadEmojiData(){if(emojiDataCache){return Promise.resolve(emojiDataCache);}return fetch('/data/emojis.min.json').then(response=>response.json()).then(data=>{emojiDataCache=data;return data;}).catch(error=>{console.error('加载 Emoji 数据失败:',error);return [];});}function createSearchResultBox(){const searchForm=document.getElementById('searchForm');if(!searchForm)return null;let resultBox=document.getElementById('searchResultBox');if(!resultBox){resultBox=document.createElement('div');resultBox.id='searchResultBox';resultBox.className='searchResultBox';searchForm.appendChild(resultBox);}return resultBox;}function showSearchResults(results,query){const resultBox=createSearchResultBox();if(!resultBox)return;if(results.length===0){resultBox.innerHTML='<div class="resItem">无搜索结果</div>';resultBox.style.display='block';return;}const html=results.map(item=>{const emoji=item.em||item.emoji||'';const name=item.n||item.name||'';const desc=item.desc||item.description||'';const keywords=item.kw||item.keywords||[];const highlightedName=highlightText(name,query);const highlightedDesc=highlightText(desc,query);const highlightedKeywords=keywords.map(keyword=>highlightText(keyword,query)).join(',');return `<a href="/emoji/${item.sl||item.slug}.html" class="resItem"><span class="resItemEmoji">${emoji}</span><span class="resItemMain"><span class="resItemName">${highlightedName}</span><span class="resItemDesc">${highlightedDesc}</span><span class="resItemDesc">tags:${highlightedKeywords}</span></span><span class="resItemSide"><button class="commonButton isSecondary isSmall jsCopyButton" aria-label="复制" data-emoji="${emoji}">复制</button></span></a>`;}).join('');resultBox.innerHTML=html;resultBox.style.display='block';}function highlightText(text,query){if(!text||!query||query.trim()===''){return text;}const escapedQuery=query.replace(/[.*+?^${}()|[\]\\]/g,'\\$&');const regex=new RegExp(`(${escapedQuery})`,'gi');return text.replace(regex,'<span class="resItemHighlight">$1</span>');}function hideSearchResults(){const resultBox=document.getElementById('searchResultBox');if(resultBox){resultBox.style.display='none';}}function showSearchLoading(){const resultBox=createSearchResultBox();if(!resultBox)return;resultBox.innerHTML='<div class="resItem" style="text-align:center;padding:10px;">加载中...</div>';resultBox.style.display='block';}function searchEmojis(query){if(!emojiDataCache||query.trim()===''){return [];}query=query.toLowerCase().trim();return emojiDataCache.filter(item=>{const emoji=(item.em||item.emoji||'').toLowerCase();const name=(item.n||item.name||'').toLowerCase();const description=(item.desc||item.description||'').toLowerCase();const keywords=(item.kw||item.keywords||[]).join(' ').toLowerCase();const code=(item.cd||item.code||'').toLowerCase();return emoji.includes(query)||name.includes(query)||description.includes(query)||keywords.includes(query)||code.includes(query);}).slice(0,10);}function handleSearchInput(e){const query=e.target.value;selectedResultIndex=-1;if(query.trim()===''){hideSearchResults();return;}showSearchLoading();loadEmojiData().then(()=>{const results=searchEmojis(query);showSearchResults(results,query);});}function performSearch(query){if(!query||query.trim()===''){hideSearchResults();return;}if(emojiDataCache){const results=searchEmojis(query);showSearchResults(results,query);}else{showSearchLoading();loadEmojiData().then(()=>{const results=searchEmojis(query);showSearchResults(results,query);});}}function handleSearchKeydown(e){const resultBox=document.getElementById('searchResultBox');if(!resultBox||resultBox.style.display==='none'){return;}const items=resultBox.querySelectorAll('.resItem');if(items.length===0){return;}switch(e.key){case 'ArrowDown':e.preventDefault();selectedResultIndex=Math.min(selectedResultIndex+1,items.length-1);updateSelectedResult(items);break;case 'ArrowUp':e.preventDefault();selectedResultIndex=Math.max(selectedResultIndex-1,0);updateSelectedResult(items);break;case 'Enter':e.preventDefault();if(selectedResultIndex>=0&&selectedResultIndex<items.length){const selectedItem=items[selectedResultIndex];if(selectedItem&&selectedItem.href){window.location.href=selectedItem.href;}}break;case 'Escape':hideSearchResults();e.target.blur();break;}}function updateSelectedResult(items){items.forEach((item,index)=>{if(index===selectedResultIndex){item.classList.add('isSelected');item.scrollIntoView({block:'nearest'});}else{item.classList.remove('isSelected');}});}function initShare(){document.body.addEventListener('click',(e)=>{const button=e.target.closest('.jsShareButton');if(button){e.preventDefault();e.stopPropagation();showSharePanel();}});}function createSharePanel(){const overlay=document.createElement('div');overlay.className='sharePanelOverlay';overlay.id='sharePanelOverlay';document.body.appendChild(overlay);const panel=document.createElement('div');panel.className='sharePanel';panel.id='sharePanel';panel.innerHTML=`<div class="sharePanelHeader"><span class="sharePanelTitle">分享到</span><button class="sharePanelClose" aria-label="关闭">×</button></div><div class="sharePanelGrid"><button class="sharePanelItem" data-type="wechat"><span class="sharePanelIcon isWechat">💬</span><span class="sharePanelLabel">微信</span></button><button class="sharePanelItem" data-type="weibo"><span class="sharePanelIcon isWeibo">📢</span><span class="sharePanelLabel">微博</span></button><button class="sharePanelItem" data-type="twitter"><span class="sharePanelIcon isTwitter">🐦</span><span class="sharePanelLabel">Twitter</span></button><button class="sharePanelItem" data-type="copy"><span class="sharePanelIcon isCopy">📋</span><span class="sharePanelLabel">复制链接</span></button></div><div class="sharePanelCopyLink"><input type="text" id="shareLinkInput" readonly><button class="commonButton isSecondary isSmall" id="shareCopyLinkBtn">复制</button></div>`;document.body.appendChild(panel);overlay.addEventListener('click',hideSharePanel);panel.querySelector('.sharePanelClose').addEventListener('click',hideSharePanel);panel.querySelectorAll('.sharePanelItem').forEach(item=>{item.addEventListener('click',()=>handleShare(item.dataset.type));});panel.querySelector('#shareCopyLinkBtn').addEventListener('click',()=>{const input=document.getElementById('shareLinkInput');copyToClipboard(input.value);showToast('链接已复制');});return{panel,overlay};}function showSharePanel(){let panel=document.getElementById('sharePanel');let overlay=document.getElementById('sharePanelOverlay');if(!panel||!overlay){const elements=createSharePanel();panel=elements.panel;overlay=elements.overlay;}const input=document.getElementById('shareLinkInput');if(input){input.value=window.location.href;}overlay.classList.add('isShow');panel.classList.add('isShow');disablePageScroll();}function hideSharePanel(){const panel=document.getElementById('sharePanel');const overlay=document.getElementById('sharePanelOverlay');if(panel)panel.classList.remove('isShow');if(overlay)overlay.classList.remove('isShow');enablePageScroll();}function handleShare(type){const url=encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);const title=encodeURIComponent(document.title);const desc=encodeURIComponent(document.querySelector('meta[name="description"]')?.content||'');let shareUrl='';switch(type){case 'wechat':showToast('请截图分享到微信');hideSharePanel();break;case 'weibo':shareUrl=`https://service.weibo.com/share/share.php?url=${url}&title=${title}`;window.open(shareUrl,'_blank','width=600,height=400');hideSharePanel();break;case 'twitter':shareUrl=`https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=${url}&text=${title}`;window.open(shareUrl,'_blank','width=600,height=400');hideSharePanel();break;case 'copy':copyToClipboard(window.location.href);showToast('链接已复制');hideSharePanel();break;}}})()